Package edu.biu.scapi.comm.multiPartyComm

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MultipartyCommunicationSetup
    The MultipartyCommunicationSetup interface manages the common functionality of all multiparty communications.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActiveMQMultipartyCommunicationSetup
    This class implements the multiparty communication uses the ActiveMQ implementation of JMS.
    SocketMultipartyCommunicationSetup
    This class implements a communication between multiple parties using TCP sockets.
    SSLActiveMQMultipartyCommunicationSetup
    This implementation uses ssl protocol in the multiparty JMS queue communication using the ActiveMQ implementation.
    SSLSocketMultipartyCommunicationSetup
    This class implements a communication between multiple parties using SSL sockets.
